FBIS4-62466 "drsov094_e_94008" FBIS-SOV-94-094 Daily Report 16 May 1994 UKRAINE International Affairs Closing Chernobyl Said To Need 10 Years, $6-8 Billion Closing Chernobyl Said To Need 10 Years, $6-8 Billion LD1605100394 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0947 GMT 16 May 94 LD1605100394 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondents Viktor Demidenko and Mikhail Melnik] [Text] Kiev May 16 ITAR-TASS -- Ukraine needs ten years and at least six to eight billion dollars to close down the Chernobyl nuclear power station, Ukrainian Vice-Premier Valeriy Shmarov told a press conference here today. He added that the final decision on the Chernobyl nuclear power station is expected to be made at the Group of Seven countries' summit this summer.
